      <para>Each property of the <see cref="T:System.Drawing.SystemFonts" /> class returns a <see cref="T:System.Drawing.Font" /> used to display text in a particular Windows display element, such as the title bar of a window. These fonts reflect the current settings in Control Panel.</para>
    </remarks>
    <summary>
      <attribution license="cc4" from="Microsoft" modified="false" />
      <para>Specifies the fonts used to display text in Windows display elements.</para>
    </summary>
  </Docs>
